Name: Overdose WW2
About the game: What is Overdose WW2 Overdose WW2 is a story set in an alternate timeline. Game Modes The game comes with a single-player story mode at launch. After the game release, there will be Zombie mode and additional content to continue the Story. Additional story missions will include a plot independent of the main game. 1944 One of the paratroopers, who attacked towards Berlin, lands in a region far from his unit. Trying to reach his goal by exiting the difficult enemy zone, Er.Miles captures a few important plans of the enemy. Try to deliver the information you have to the closest allied unit among the enemies on this difficult road that you set out on your own.
